{"tid":773950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【灣仔高鐘】警掃色情會所拘14「高鐘妹」　帳單揭春宵一刻九萬蚊","createTime":"2018-08-10T02:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T09:12:12.000Z","uid":83125,"like":168,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e36696abbea2cf94c36960263317c80bb30f89","tid":773950,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T02:59:48.000Z","msg":"警方灣仔反三合會行動組聯同灣仔特別職務隊人員，於昨日(8日)深夜突擊搜查灣仔謝婓道一間樓上私人會所，拘捕14名內地女子及1男1女負責人(29歲至45歲)。據知，上址以會所為名，跑高鐘為實。<br />\n<br />\n而警員在上址檢獲一批現金及多張帳單，其中一張單達9萬多元，紀錄消費包括1萬9千多元的5支「麥卡倫18年」威士忌、48支藍妹啤酒，另外再加上海鮮、果盤及萬多元的服務費。另一張萬多元的帳單則紀錄2支波爾多紅酒、果仁及食物等消費。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/105705_d623ad54de63518645cac30dd5d9b93f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F105705_d623ad54de63518645cac30dd5d9b93f.png&h=69582291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員檢獲一張9萬多元的帳單。(陳永武攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/105840_8720a6cd4e26963f5f868c87060edd75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F105840_8720a6cd4e26963f5f868c87060edd75.png&h=b6a22fcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一張萬多元的帳單則紀錄2支波爾多紅酒、果仁及食物等消費。（陳永武攝）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/10/105848_4d8b745c66e1dcca4484088b5c2bc20f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F10%2F105848_4d8b745c66e1dcca4484088b5c2bc20f.png&h=32a9cffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Charge<br />\nSEAFOOD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"35f82fb489321f438a1a5361e62d0ecd7c7258b2","tid":773950,"uid":83125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime